{"h0a4b9c00g0be4g4e22g8eeag31656dbaae28": ["*The drum sits in silence.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "99f10f19-48d4-2d22-0ade-84852a073765"], "h54c45eb9g6370g4e19g8cdfga3943f972b8c": ["*The drum sits in silence.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "c4cfd2c1-01aa-06e3-5429-bf44dec9b37a"], "h075ae049g863bg4e8cg810fg7a8392ce1fda": ["*This mighty drum is powerful enough to be heard for miles. You need only strike it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "9eb0ccbf-8f7d-631c-716f-8c851c7d49a9"], "hf4095740g7e60g4b79g8e7ag29eb6ecb2cfb": ["<i>Hit the drum.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "34cde62f-e886-59c0-8227-fcc5cd0ffa0d"], "h503fe865g85e4g43f2g93bbg3fc8ea73c97d": ["*As the echo of the drum fades, silence reasserts itself.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "597a941d-338c-d114-7f21-c7c10657a8b0"], "h6eed2cbdg2ac7g4e22g8a2ega0d4d7afcb1f": ["*The distant chatter of the goblins explodes into angry shouting. They are running your way, swiftly as they can.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "fa7532b8-3c7e-bbef-4777-b8e381c4c881"], "h740dcc8ag1ac1g4e27g9110g9b3b29c58a76": ["*Chaos ignites in the ruins around you. Goblins howl and spit, clawing for their weapons.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "0f1eb59e-0fc6-7031-653c-25ad443f53fe"], "h1c06fab8g3cb2g41b0ga641gab58b6c7e703": ["<i>Break the drum so no one can use it.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "0c1de7ea-8838-13ec-3d20-a4e1cec6bc85"], "h6ab7185dg8403g4907g948cg67137d0df470": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Battlestations_WarDrum.html", "dc4f9f7e-32af-fdac-1bd2-fa2be964e589"]